snippet.title: 5 Force Fighters - Official Developer Video | Black Voices in Gaming 2024
snippet.description: Meet the developers at Kaizen Creed and learn more about the duo behind their upcoming game, 5 Force Fighters. 5 Force Fighters is a 2D fighting game with a cast of unstoppable characters, and a combat system that boasts universal offensive and defensive options. Unravel the story of 5 teens blessed with elemental powers, but cursed with scarred pasts that have led them to a common, but destructive, goal.
